latestIgtvVideos.caption: Foolproof @dysonhair Airwrap tutorial ✨ I love styling my hair like this after I wash it because it stays smooth, bouncy, and voluminous throughout the week. If I need to touch up, I go in with the curling attachment on dry hair and end up with the same results. If you’re someone who constantly styles their hair with heat but wants to minimize damage, the airwrap is an amazing investment for your hair.
